quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  18,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  18,1,sab tareef khuda hi ko hai jis ne apne bande ( Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) par ( yeh ) kitaab nazil ki aur is mein kisi terhan ki kajji ( aur paicheedgi ) nah rakhi
  18,2,seedhi ( aur salees utari ) taakay logon ko azaab sakht se jo is ki taraf se ( anay wala ) hai dry aur mominoun ko jo naik amal karte hain khushkhabri sunaye ke unn ke liye ( un ke kamon ka ) naik badla ( yani ) bahisht hai
  18,3,jis mein woh aubdul -aabaad rahen ge
  18,4,aur un logon ko bhi dry jo kehte hain ke khuda ne ( kisi ko ) beta bana liya hai
  18,5,un ko is baat ka kuch bhi ilm nahi aur nah un ke baap dada hi ko tha. ( yeh ) barri sakht baat hai jo un ke munh se nikalti hai ( aur kuch shak nahi ) ke yeh jo kehte hain mehez jhoot hai
  18,6,( ae paighambar ) agar yeh is kalaam par imaan nah layein to shayad tum ke un peechay ranj kar kar ke apne tain halaak kardo ge
  18,7,jo cheez zameen par hai hum ne is ko zameen ke liye Araish banaya hai taakay logon ki azmaish karen ke un mein kon achay amal karne wala hai
  18,8,aur jo cheez zameen par hai hum is ko ( nabood karkay ) banjar maidan kar dein ge
  18,9,kiya tum khayaal karte ho ke ghaar aur looh walay hamaray nshanyon mein se ajeeb they
  18,10,jab woh jawan ghaar mein ja rahay to kehnay lagey ke ae hamaray perwar-digaar hum par apne haan se rehmat nazil farma. aur hamaray kaam durusti ( ke samaan ) muhayya kar
  18,11,to hum ne ghaar mein kayi saal taq un ke kaanon par ( neend ka ) parda daaley ( yani un ko sulay ) rakha
  18,12,phir un ko jaga aُthaya taakay maloom karen ke jitni mddt woh ( ghaar mein ) rahay dono jamaaton mein se is ki miqdaar kis ko khoob yaad hai
  18,13,hum unn ke halaat tum se sahih sahih bayan karte hain. woh kayi jawan they jo apne perwar-digaar par imaan laaye they aur hum ne un ko aur ziyada hadaayat di thi
  18,14,aur un ke dilon ko marboot ( yani mazboot ) kardiya. jab woh ( aُth ) kharray hue to kehnay lagey ke hamara perwar-digaar asmano aur zameen ka maalik hai. hum is ke siwa kisi ko mabood ( samajh kar ) nah pukaarain ge ( agar aisakiya ) to is waqt hum ne baeed az aqal baat kahi
  18,15,un hamari qoum ke logon ne is ke siwa aur mabood bana rakhay hain. bhala yeh un ( ke khuda honay ) par koi khuli Daleel kyun nahi laatay. to is se ziyada kon zalim hai jo khuda par jhoot iftira kere
  18,16,aur jab tum ne un ( mushrikon ) se aur jin ki yeh khuda ke siwa ibadat karte hain un se kinara karliya hai to ghaar mein chal raho tumhara perwar-digaar tumahray liye apni rehmat wasee kardey ga aur tumahray kamon mein aasani ( ke samaan ) muhayya kere ga
  18,17,aur jab Sooraj niklay to tum dekho ke ( dhoop ) un ke ghaar se dahni taraf simat jaye aur jab ghuroob ho to un se baen taraf katra jaye aur woh is ke maidan mein they. yeh khuda ki nshanyon mein se hain. jis ko khuda hadaayat day ya woh hadaayat yab hai aur jis ko gumraah kere to tum is ke liye koi dost raah bitanay wala nah pao ge
  18,18,aur tum un ko khayaal karo ke jaag rahay hain halaank woh sotay hain. aur hum un ko dayen aur baen karvat badlatay they. aur un ka kutta chokhat par dono haath phelaaye hue tha. agar tum un ko jhaank kar dekhte to peeth phair kar bhaag jatay aur un se dehshat mein aajate
  18,19,aur is terhan hum ne un ko uthaya taakay aapas mein aik dosray se daryaft karen. aik kehnay walay ne kaha ke tum ( yahan ) kitni muddat rahay? unhon ne kaha ke aik din ya is se bhi kam. unhon ne kaha ke jitni muddat tum rahay ho tumhara perwar-digaar hi is ko khoob jaanta hai. to apne mein se kisi ko yeh rupiya day kar shehar ko bhaijho woh dekhe ke nafees khana kon sa hai to is mein se khana le aeye aur aahista aahista aeye jaye aur tumhara haal kisi ko nah betaye
  18,20,agar woh tum par dustarus paleen ge to tumhe sangsar kar dein ge ya phir apne mazhab mein daakhil karlen ge aur is waqt tum kabhi Falah nahi pao ge
  18,21,aur isi terhan hum ne ( logon ko ) un ( ke haal ) se khabardaar kardiya taakay woh jaanen ke khuda ka wada sacha hai aur yeh ke qayamat ( jis ka wadakiya jata hai ) is mein kuch shak nahi. is waqt log un ke baray mein baahum jhagrnay lagey aur kehnay lagey ke un ( ke ghaar ) par imarat bana do. un ka perwar-digaar un ( ke haal ) se khoob waaqif hai. jo log un ke muamlay mein ghalba rakhtay they woh kehnay lagey ke hum un ( ke ghaar ) par masjid banayen ge
  18,22,( baaz log ) atkal pacho kahin ge ke woh teen they ( aur ) choutha un ka kutta tha. aur ( baaz ) kahin ge ke woh paanch they aur chhata un ka kutta tha. aur ( baaz ) kahin ge ke woh saat they aur aathwan un ka kutta tha. keh do ke mera perwar-digaar hi un ke shumaar se khoob waaqif hai un ko jantay bhi hain to thoray hi log ( jantay hain ) to tum un ( ke muamlay ) mein guftagu nah karna magar sarsari si guftagu. aur nah un ke baray mein un mein kisi se kuch daryaft hi karna
  18,23,aur kisi kaam ki nisbat nah kehna ke mein usay kal kardoon ga
  18,24,magar ( Insha allah keh kar yani agar ) khuda chahay to ( kardoon ga ) aur jab khuda ka naam lena bhool jao to yaad anay par le lau. aur keh do ke umeed hai ke mera perwar-digaar mujhe is se bhi ziyada hadaayat ki baatein betaye
  18,25,aur ashaab kahaf apne ghaar mein no oopar teen so saal rahay
  18,26,keh do ke jitni mddt woh rahay usay khuda hi khoob jaanta hai. isi ko asmano aur zameen ki posheeda baatein ( maloom ) hain. wohkiya khoob dekhnay wala aurkiya khoob suneney wala hai. is ke siwa un ka koi karsaaz nahi aur nah woh apne hukum mein kisi shareek ko karta hai
  18,27,aur apne perwar-digaar ki kitaab jo tumahray paas bhaije jati hai parhte raha karo. is ki baton ko koi badalny wala nahi. aur is ke siwa tum kahin panah ki jagah bhi nahi pao ge
  18,28,aur jo log subah o shaam apne perwar-digaar ko pkarte aur is ki khushnodi ke taalib hain. un ke sath sabr karte raho. aur tumhari nigehain un mein ( guzar kar aur taraf ) nah dorhin ke tum aaraish zindagani duniya ke khawastgah hojao. aur jis shakhs ke dil ko hum ne apni yaad se ghaafil kardiya hai aur woh apni khwahish ki pairwi karta hai aur is ka kaam hadd se barh gaya hai is ka kaha nah maanna
  18,29,aur keh do ke ( logo ) yeh quran tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se brhq hai to jo chahay imaan laaye aur jo chahay kafir rahay. hum ne zaalmon ke liye dozakh ki aag tayyar kar rakhi hai jis ki qanatain un ko ghair rahi hon gi. aur agar faryaad karen ge to aisay kholtey hue pani se un ki dadrsi ki jaye gi ( jo ) pighlay hue tanbay ki terhan ( garam hoga aur jo ) monhon ko bhon daaley ga ( un ke peenay ka ) pani bhi bura aur aaraam gaah bhi buri
  18,30,( aur ) jo imaan laaye aur kaam bhi naik karte rahay to hum naik kaam karne walon ka ajar zaya nahi karte
  18,31,aisay logon ke liye hamesha rehne ke baagh hain jin mein un ke ( mehloon ke ) neechay nehrain beh rahi hain un ko wahan sonay ke kangon pahnaye jayen ge aur woh bareek Deeba aur Atlas ke sabz kapray pehna karen ge ( aur ) takhton par takyay laga kar betha karen ge. (kiya ) khoob badla aur (kiya ) khoob aaraam gaah hai
  18,32,aur un se do shakhson ka haal bayan karo jin mein se aik hum ne angoor ke do baagh ( inayat ) kiye they aur un ke gurda gird khajoron ke darakht laga diye they aur un ke darmain khaiti peda kar di thi
  18,33,dono baagh ( kasrat se ) phal laatay. aur is ( ki pedawar ) mein kisi terhan ki kami nah hoti aur dono mein hum ne aik neher bhi jari kar rakhi thi
  18,34,aur ( is terhan ) is ( shakhs ) ko ( un ki ) pedawar ( millti rehti ) thi to ( aik din ) jab ke woh apne dost se baatein kar raha tha kehnay laga ke mein tum se maal o dolat mein bhi ziyada hon aur jthe ( aur jamaat ) ke lehaaz se bhi ziyada izzat wala hon
  18,35,aur ( aisi shakhiyon ) se apne haq mein zulm karta howa apne baagh mein daakhil howa. kehnay laga ke mein nahi khayaal karta ke yeh baagh kabhi tabah ho
  18,36,aur nah khayaal karta hon ke qayamat barpaa ho. aur agar mein apne perwar-digaar ki taraf lotaya bhi jaoon to ( wahan ) zaroor is se achi jagah paon ga
  18,37,to is ka dost jo is se guftagu kar raha tha kehnay laga kekiya tum is ( khuda ) se kufar karte ho jis ne tum ko matti se pedakiya phir nutfay se phir tumhe poora mard banaya
  18,38,magar mein to yeh kehta hon ke khuda hi mera perwar-digaar hai aur mein apne perwar-digaar ke sath kisi ko shareek nahi karta
  18,39,aur ( bhala ) jab tum apne baagh mein daakhil hue to tum ne mashah allah quwwata illalbillah kyun nah kaha. agar tum mujhe maal o aulaad mein apne se kamtar dekhte ho
  18,40,to ajab nahi ke mera perwar-digaar mujhe tumahray baagh se behtar ataa farmaiye aur is ( tumahray baagh ) par aasman se aafat bhaij day to woh saaf maidan hojaye
  18,41,ya is ( ki neher ) ka pani gehra hojaye to phir tum usay nah laa sako
  18,42,aur is ke mewoon ko azaab ne aa ghera aur woh apni chatriyon par gir kar reh gaya. to jo maal is ne is par kharchkiya tha is par ( hasrat se ) haath milnay laga aur kehnay laga ke kash mein apne perwar-digaar ke sath kisi ko shareek nah banata
  18,43,( is waqt ) khuda ke siwa koi jamaat is ki madadgaar nah hui aur nah woh badla le saka
  18,44,yahan ( se saabit howa ke ) hukoomat sab khuday-e brhq hi ki hai. isi ka sila behtar aur ( isi ka ) badla acha hai
  18,45,aur un se duniya ki zindagi ki misaal bhi bayan kardo ( woh aisi hai ) jaisay pani jisay hum ne aasman se barsaya. to is ke sath zameen ki roedgi mil gayi. phir woh choora choora hogayi ke hawae usay urati phurti hain. aur khuda to har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai
  18,46,maal aur betay to duniya ki zindagi ki ( ronaqe o ) zeenat hain. aur naikian jo baqi rehne wali hain woh sawab ke lehaaz se tumahray perwar-digaar ke haan bohat achi aur umeed ke lehaaz se bohat behtar hain
  18,47,aur jis din hum pahoron ko chalayein ge aur tum zameen ko saaf maidan dekho ge aur un ( logon ko ) hum jama karlen ge to un mein se kisi ko bhi nahi choden ge
  18,48,aur sab tumahray perwar-digaar ke samnay saf bandh kar laaye jayen ge ( to hum un se kahin ge ke ) jis terhan hum ne tum ko pehli baar pedakiya tha ( isi terhan aaj ) tum hamaray samnay aeye lekin tum ne to yeh khayaal kar rakha tha ke hum ne tumahray liye ( qayamat ka ) koi waqt muqarrar hi nahikiya
  18,49,aur ( amlon ki ) kitaab ( khol kar ) rakhi jaye gi to tum gunahgaaron ko dekho ge ke jo kuch is mein ( likha ) hoga is se dar rahay hon ge aur kahin ge haae shamat yeh kaisi kitaab hai ke nah choti baat ko chodthee hai nah barri ko. ( koi baat bhi nahi ) magar usay likh rakha hai. aur jo amal kiye hon ge sab ko haazir payen ge. aur tumhara perwar-digaar kisi par zulm nahi kere ga
  18,50,aur jab hum ne firshton ko hukum diya ke aadam ko sajda karo to sab ne sajdakiya magar iblees ( ne nahkiya ) woh jaanat mein se tha to apne perwar-digaar ke hukum se bahar hogaya.kiya tum is ko aur is ki aulaad ko mere siwa dost banatay ho. halaank woh tumahray dushman hain ( aur shetan ki dosti ) zaalmon ke liye ( khuda ki dosti ka ) bura badal hai
  18,51,mein ne un ko nah to asmano aur zameen ke peda karne ke waqt bulaya tha aur nah khud un ke peda karne ke waqt. aur mein aisa nah tha ke gumraah karne walon ko madadgaar banata
  18,52,aur jis din khuda farmaiye ga ke ( ab ) mere sharikon ko jin ki nisbat tum gumaan ( al-wahiyat ) rakhtay they bulaao to woh un ke bulayen ge magar woh un ko kuch jawab nah den ge. aur hum un ke beech mein aik halakat ki jagah bnadin ge
  18,53,aur gunehgaar log dozakh ko dekhen ge to yaqeen karlen ge ke woh is mein parney walay hain. aur is se bachney ka koi rasta nah payen ge
  18,54,aur hum ne is quran mein logon ( ke samjhane ) ke liye terhan terhan ki misalein bayan farmai hain. lekin ensaan sab cheezon se barh kar jhagralu hai
  18,55,aur logon ke paas jab hadaayat aagai to un ko kis cheez ne manakiya ke imaan layein. aur apne perwar-digaar se bakhshish mangeen. bajuz is ke ke ( is baat ke munhtazir hon ke ) inhen bhi pehloo ka sa maamla paish aeye ya un par azaab samnay aa mojood ho
  18,56,aur hum jo payghambaroon ko bheja karte hain to sirf is liye ke ( logon ko khuda ki nematon ki ) khushkhabriyan sunaein aur ( azaab se ) dra-ayn. aur jo kafir hain woh baatil ki ( sanad ) se jhagra karte hain taakay is se haq ko phsla den aur unhon ne hamari aayton ko aur jis cheez se un ko daraya jata hai hansi bana liya
  18,57,aur is se zalim kon jis ko is ke perwar-digaar ke kalaam se samjhaya gaya to uss ne is se munh phair liya. aur jo aamaal woh agay krchka is ko bhool gaya. hum ne un ke dilon par parday daal diye ke usay samajh nah saken. aur kaanon mein saqal ( peda kardiya hai ke sun nah saken ) aur agar tum un ko raste ki taraf bulaao to kabhi raste par nah ayen ge
  18,58,aur tumhara perwar-digaar bakhsnay wala sahib rehmat hai. agar woh un ke krtoton par un ko pakarney lagey to un par jhat azaab bhaij day. magar un ke liye aik waqt ( muqarrar kar rakha ) hai ke is ke azaab se koi panah ki jagah nah payen ge
  18,59,aur yeh bastiyan ( jo weraan pari hain ) jab unhon ne ( kufar se ) zulmkiya to hum ne un ko tabah kar diya. aur un ki tabahi ke liye aik waqt muqarrar kardiya tha
  18,60,aur jab moose ne apne shagird se kaha ke jab taq do daryaaon ke milnay ki jagah nah poanch jaoon hatnay ka nahi khuwa barson chalta rahon
  18,61,jab un ke milnay ke maqam par puhanche to apni machhli bhool gay to is ne darya mein surang ki terhan apna rasta bnalya
  18,62,jab agay chalay to ( moose ne ) apne shagird se kaha ke hamaray liye khana lao. is safar se hum ko bohat takan hogayi hai
  18,63,( is ne ) kaha ke bhala aap ne dekha ke jab hum ne pathar ke sath aaraamkiya tha to mein machhli ( wahein ) bhool gaya. aur mujhe ( aap se ) is ka zikar karna shetan ne bhala diya. aur is ne ajab terhan se darya mein apna rasta liya
  18,64,( moose ne ) kaha yahi to ( woh maqam ) hai jisay hum talaash karte they to woh apne paon ke nishaan dekhte dekhte lout gay
  18,65,( wahan ) unhon ne hamaray bundon mein se aik bandah dekha jis ko hum ne apne haan se rehmat ( yani nabuwat ya Nemat Wilayat ) di thi aur apne paas se ilm bakhsha tha
  18,66,moose ne un se ( jin ka naam khizar tha ) kaha ke jo ilm ( khuda ki taraf se ) aap ko sikhaya gaya hai agar aap is mein se mujhe kuch bhalai ( ki baatein ) skhayin to mein aap ke sath rahon
  18,67,( khizar ne ) kaha ke tum mere sath reh kar sabr nahi krsko ge
  18,68,aur jis baat ki tumhe khabar hi nahi is par sabr kar bhi kyun kar saktay ho
  18,69,( moose ne ) kaha khuda ne chaha to aap mujhe sabir pai-yay ga. aur mein aap ke irshad ke khilaaf nahi karoon ga
  18,70,( khizar ne ) kaha ke agar tum mere sath rehna chaho to ( shart yeh hai ) mujh se koi baat nah poochna jab taq mein khud is ka zikar tum se nah karoon
  18,71,to dono chal parre. yahan taq ke jab kashti mein sawaar hue to ( khizar ne ) kashti ko phaar dala. ( moose ne ) kahakiya aap ne is liye pharha hai ke sawaron ko ghark kar dein yeh to aap ne barri ( ajeeb ) baat ki
  18,72,( khizar ne ) kaha.kiya mein ne nahi kaha tha ke tum mere sath sabr nah krsko ge
  18,73,( moose ne ) kaha ke jo bhool mujh se hui is par muwakhza nah kijiye aur mere muamlay mein mujh par mushkil nah dalye
  18,74,phir dono chalay. yahan taq ke ( raste mein ) aik larka mila to ( khizar ne ) ussay maar dala. ( moose ne ) kaha ke aap ne aik be gunah shakhs ko na-haq baghair qisaas ke maar dala. ( yeh to ) aap ne buri baat ki
  18,75,( khizar ne ) kahakiya mein ne nahi kaha tha ke tum se mere sath sabr nahi krsko ge
  18,76,unhon ne kaha ke agar mein is ke baad ( phir ) koi baat pouchon ( yani aitraaz karoon ) to mujhe apne sath nah rkhiye ga ke aap meri taraf se izr ( ke qubool karne mein Ghayat ) ko poanch gay
  18,77,phir dono chalay. yahan taq ke aik gaon walon ke paas puhanche aur un se khana talabkiya. unhon ne un ki ziyafat karne se inkaar kar diya. phir unhon ne wahan aik deewar dekhi jo ( jhuk kar ) gira chahti thi. khizar ne is ko seedha kar diya. moose ne kaha agar aap chahtay to un se ( is ka ) muawza letay ( taakay khanay ka kaam chalta )
  18,78,khizar ne kaha ab mujh mein aur tujh mein alehadgi. ( magar ) jin baton par tum sabr nah kar sakay mein un ka tumhe bhaid betaye deta hon
  18,79,( ke woh jo ) kashti ( thi ) ghareeb logon ki thi jo darya mein mehnat ( karkay yani kashtiyan chala kar gzarh ) karte they. aur un ke samnay ( ki taraf ) aik badshah tha jo har aik kashti ko zabardasti chean laita tha to mein ne chaha ke usay aib daar kardoon ( taakay woh usay ghasab nah kar sakay )
  18,80,aur woh jo larka tha is ke maa baap dinon momin they hamein andesha howa ke ( woh bara ho kar badkirdar hota kahin ) un ko sar kashi aur kufar mein nah phansa day
  18,81,to hum ne chaha ke un ka perwar-digaar is ki jagah un ko aur ( bchch_h ) ataa farmaiye jo pak tiniti mein aur mohabbat mein is se behtar ho
  18,82,aur woh jo deewar thi so woh do yateem larkoon ki thi ( jo ) shehar mein ( rehtay they ) aur is ke neechay un ka khazana ( madfoon ) tha aur un ka baap aik naik bakht aadmi tha. to tumahray perwar-digaar ne chaha ke woh apni jawani ko poanch jayen aur ( phir ) apna khazana nikalen. yeh tumahray perwar-digaar ki meharbani hai. aur yeh kaam mein ne apni taraf se nahi kiye. yeh un baton ka raaz hai jin par tum sabr nah kar sakay
  18,83,aur tum se zwalqrnin ke baray mein daryaft karte hain. keh do ke mein is ka kisi qader haal tumhe parh kar sunataa hon
  18,84,hum ne is ko zameen mein barri dustarus di thi aur har terhan ka samaan ataakiya tha
  18,85,to is ne ( safar ka ) aik samaankiya
  18,86,yahan taq ke jab Sooraj ke ghuroob honay ki jagah pouncha to usay aisa paaya ke aik keechar ki nadi mein doob raha hai aur is ( nadi ) ke paas aik qoum dekhi. hum ne kaha zwalqrnin! tum un ko khuwa takleef do khuwa un ( ke baray ) mein bhalai ikhtiyar karo ( dono baton mein tum ko qudrat hai )
  18,87,zwalqrnin ne kaha ke jo ( kufar o badkardari se ) zulm kere ga usay hum azaab den ge. phir ( jab ) woh apne perwar-digaar ki taraf lotaya jaye ga to woh bhi usay bُra azaab day ga
  18,88,aur jo imaan laaye ga aur amal naik kere ga is ke liye bohat acha badla hai. aur hum apne muamlay mein ( is par kisi terhan ki sakhti nahi karen ge balkay ) is se naram baat kahin ge
  18,89,phir is ne aik aur samaan ( safar ka )kiya
  18,90,yahan taq ke Sooraj ke tulu honay ke maqam par pouncha to dekha ke woh aisay logon par tulu karta hai jin ke liye hum ne Sooraj ke is taraf koi oot nahi banai thi
  18,91,( haqeeqat haal ) yun ( thi ) aur jo kuch is ke paas tha hum ko sab ki khabar thi
  18,92,phir is ne aik aur samaankiya
  18,93,yahan taq ke do dewaron ke darmain pouncha to dekha ke un ke is taraf kuch log hain ke baat ko samajh nahi satke
  18,94,un logon ne kaha zwalqrnin! yajooj aur majooj zameen mein fasaad karte rehtay hain bhala hum aap ke liye kharch ( ka intizam ) kar dein ke aap hamaray aur un ke darmain aik deewar khech den
  18,95,zwalqrnin ne kaha ke kharch ka jo Maqdoor khuda ne mujhe bakhsha hai woh bohat acha hai. tum mujhe qowat ( baazu ) se madad do. mein tumahray aur un ke darmain aik mazboot oot bana dun ga
  18,96,to tum lohay ke ( barray barray ) takhtay lao ( chunancha kaam jari kardiya gaya ) yahan taq ke jab is ne dono pahoron ke darmain ( ka hissa ) barabar kar diya. aur kaha ke ( ab usay ) dhonko . yahan taq ke jab is ko ( dhonk dhonk ) kar aag kar diya to kaha ke ( ab ) mere paas tanbah lao is par pighla kar daal dun
  18,97,phir un mein yeh qudrat nah rahi ke is par charh saken aur nah yeh taaqat rahi ke is mein naqb laga saken
  18,98,bola ke yeh mere perwar-digaar ki meharbani hai. jab mere perwar-digaar ka wada aa pohnchay ga to is ko ( dhaa kar ) hamwar kardey ga aur mere perwar-digaar ka wada sacha hai
  18,99,( is roz ) hum un ko chore den ge ke ( roye zameen par phail kar ) aik dosray mein ghis jayen ge aur sor phonka jaye ga to hum sab ko jama karlen ge
  18,100,aur uss roz jahannum ko kafiroon ke samnay layein ge
  18,101,jin ki ankhen meri yaad se parday mein theen aur woh suneney ki taaqat nahi rakhtay they
  18,102,kiya kafir yeh khayaal karte hain ke woh hamaray bundon ko hamaray siwa ( apna ) karsaaz banayen ge ( to hum khafa nahi hon ge ) hum ne ( aisay ) kafiroon ke liye jahannum ki ( mehmani ) tayyar kar rakhi hai
  18,103,keh do ke hum tumhe bitayen jo amlon ke lehaaz se barray nuqsaan mein hain
  18,104,woh log jin ki sae duniya ki zindagi mein barbaad hogayi. aur woh yeh samjhay hue hain ke achay kaam kar rahay hain
  18,105,yeh woh log hain jinhon ne apne perwar-digaar ki aayton aur is ke samnay jaane se inkaarkiya to un ke aamaal zaya hogaye aur hum qayamat ke din un ke liye kuch bhi wazan qaim nahi karen ge
  18,106,yeh un ki saza hai ( yani ) jahannum. is liye ke unhon ne kufarkiya aur hamari aayton aur hamaray payghambaroon ki hansi udai
  18,107,jo log imaan laaye aur amal naik kiye un ke liye bahisht ke baagh mehmani hon ge
  18,108,hamesha un mein rahen ge aur wahan se makaan badalna nah chahain ge
  18,109,keh do ke agar samandar mere perwar-digaar ki baton ke ( likhnay ke ) liye siyahi ho to qabal is ke ke mere perwar-digaar ki baatein tamam hon samandar khatam hojaye agarchay hum waisa hi aur ( samandar ) is ki madad ko layein
  18,110,keh do ke mein tumhari terhan ka aik bashar hon. ( Albata ) meri taraf wahi aati hai ke tumhara mabood ( wohi ) aik mabood hai. to jo shakhs apne perwar-digaar se milnay ki umeed rakhay chahiye ke amal naik kere aur apne perwar-digaar ki ibadat mein kisi ko shareek nah banaye
